content: Yeah, I know you're just an assistant. I was just mentioning that I'm looking forward to our Sunday morning breakfast tradition because it's something I really enjoy. Anyway, thanks for the pasta recipe! I'll make sure to pass it along to my mom. One more thing - do you have any advice on how to prioritize tasks and manage my workload better? My friend Alex has been giving me some tips, but I'd love to hear more suggestions.
